gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Clippers 123, Spurs 83
gameRecap.excerpt: The Clippers defeated the Spurs, 123-83. Kawhi Leonard led all scorers with 21 points for the Clippers, while Paul George and Russell Westbrook each added 19 points in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 11 points and five rebounds for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Clippers improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 1-2.
